Hey what's going on?  I haven't posted in here in forever.  Nothing much is really new with me that's for sure.  Single more than ever which sucks real bad.  Mostly just working.  Trying to make some cash.  Hmm so what have I been doing...  Last weekend we went bowling with Tina and Jeff that was fun.  I have hung out with Josh a couple of times, he is cute.  Talked to Josh T.  which made me happy.  Haven't really done a whole lot of anything.  We went to fushion with Tina and Nikki and Mark, Michelle, and Mindy were there and I saw Sarah Robertson..  That's pretty much it.  Now I am babysitting and I can't use my fucking phone argh.

I mean I haven't been in here in a while.  Work is going pretty good.  Blah.  I mean Kevin broke up with me for his ex which I am not too happy about, but it happens so its all good gangsta. So I mean if there are any single men out there you know where I'm at.  Dang.  I am so freakin tired. BLAH.
I am not very happy right now...

I haven't updated in a while I am sure you are sad whoever the fuck reads this, probably no one.  Blah I have to leave for work in like a half hour and I am not ready.  Oh well.  Amy finally got her car back yesterday and I am so fucking glad.  Blah staying up til 7 and getting up at 930 isnt fun.  I am so tired.  Oh well I don't care.  I love hanging out with Kevin even though he tells me I don't like him which is totally untrue.  He's silly.  Ok well that's all the fun for now I am going to go and try and wake up his lazy ass.  Peace out nigga

I can't wait to go to the taste of chaos I am so fucking excited.  Dang.

Blah blah blah.  I am so tired for some reason and I already feel like not going to work tomorrow.  I mean I am sure I will, it's like the easiest job ever.  I have already worked there almost 2 months and I haven't missed or been late or anything so I'm good.  Hhhhmmm so what have I been up to?  Well a couple of weeks ago we hung out at Claude's, that was fun.  Claude is such a fun guy to hang out with.  I enjoyed that.  It was me, Amy, Kati and Claude.  Me and Claude played some pool and him and Kati ran mad fast on the treadmill.  Um what else oh we went to wendy's the other day and James was with Lindsay in front of us.  He actually talked to us I didn't think he would.  He said he would give me and Amy a ride in his new convertable.  I missed James, I hadn't seen him in forever.  The other day me and Amy and Kati went to the mall with Chris and his friend Jesse.  I didn't think I would like him and I don't.  He's an asshole.  We have been hanging out with Butch too.  We went to applebees and saw Barb.  Her hair is so damn cute, I am jealous.  I stayed at Kevins last night I don't really remember what we did, but we stayed up til 6 in the morning.  I have been here all day and he asked me to stay again.  Blah he is so cute.  I really like hanging out with him.  I have fun.  *sigh*  I think I like him alot.  That's good I think.  I don't know.  I hope it's good anyways.   Well I hope he thinks its good.  Hhmmm.  Ok then I am going to get in the shower which I need to do real bad so ta ta

Blah I am so bored.  What's new and I am tired as fuck.  Funk me.  I am ready for bed, but I am babysitting and I think Amy is picking me up at 4.  So I will be awake til then.  I wanted to talk to Kevin, but the bastard isn't online.  Uuuuuuuuuuuhhhhhhh.  Oh well.  Anyways... Work is going ok.  I got some new piercings.  I got my lip done again and my ears a couple of times.  My other conch even though I said I would never do that again, but I did.  Ok then fun times for now my negros.

Blah I havent updated in my journal in a long time i am so fucking lazy i have been busy working and shit  i am so fucking glad that it is friday and i dont have to get up tomorrow i am probably staying at kevins tonight fun times really is maybe some hardcore make out action

<FONT color=#ff6666>Well I haven't updated in forever.  I don't know what I have been doing, but not writing in here that's for sure.  Blah.  Work is going pretty good.  I have worked there over a month now.  It's pretty awesome I have made it that far lol.  I need the money bad,how bad?, it's real bad.  I don't know what the hell I am doing.  I have been thinking and I need to find a boyfriend.  Not just one that is going to last for like a month like the other ones, but a real one, someone that I really care about.  Only if it were that easy, but it's not. Someone who wants to be with me and that's it.  Gosh. I don't know if I could possibly make someone that happy.  Probably not.  *sigh*  Oh well.  I don't know what I want out of my life, just to be happy I guess, is that too much to ask?  Haha yes, yes it is.  Well I have a fucking class this weekend, that's going to suck hardcore.  I haven't gotten hardly any sleep lately.  Two nights last week I stayed up all night and then had to work the next day one day and had shit to do the other day.  It was worth it though, I really like Kevin.  I like hanging out with him, I hope he likes hanging out with me too.  That would be good.  I want more out of this, but I don't know if he does or when or whatever.  I'll just wait and see.  Me wait?  Haha maybe...</FONT>

Blah tomorrow is Friday I am so glad.  I am so tired.  I babysit tonight and I have to be at work at 8:15 tomorrow and work til 6:30.  Oh well.  I didn't go to bed last night.  I stayed up all night with Kevin.  I got home about 8 & took a shower.  I did fall asleep on the couch for about an hour.  So I am pretty tired.  I like Kevin.  I don't know if he knows it or not, but I do.  He is silly.  He told me he liked me too, I hope he does.  Anyways... I am real tired yeah.  My knuckles are busted open and my lips hurt real bad.

Blah it's monday which sucks, but good thing it's almost over.  So what did I do this weekend.  Well Friday I don't remember.  Saturday I babysat.  Early sunday morning I met this really cool guy, Kevin, we totally made out it was awesome.  So I went to be at like 730 and got up at 11 and then went back to bed at 2 and got up at 4.  I talked on the phone with him last night til 2 and got up at 9 this morning.  I am tired.  It's real bad.  Oh well I like talking to him.  Oh yeah and last night we met these guys at meijer, one of them looked real familar.  It was friggin Josh Lovelace, aka Cornbread.  He asked who wanted to make love.  It was funny, we went to tim hortons with them.  Wow.  Fun times.  I am ready for bed, Oh yeah and to do it, but we don't always get what we want.
Blah it is 230 I am real tired.  Oh well.  Argh fun times.
I miss Nelly Bubbles, John you suck argh!

My horoscope said I was having a 9/10 day, but I am pretty sure it friggin lied!   I am so tired I had to go to work at 8 and work til 630, which I am sure normal people work all the time.  My shoes are too small though and my feet hurt real bad.  Oh well.  I don't know.  I am so bored and there is absolutely nothing to do.  Blah argh.   I love pirates though that's for sure duh.

I have been doing alot of thinking and I don't know what the hell is wrong with me.  It's like sometimes I am normal and others I just act I don't know stupid.  It's like I want people to like me, but then I act weird and annoying.  I really don't mean to be like that.  I don't know what to do.  I mean I am a fun person sometimes.  I don't know why I can't be like that at least most of the time.  I know I am still going to have my bad days everyone does.  I just need to be more calm.  Maybe see a therapist.   Maybe they can figure out what my problem is.  I need to take a deep breath and chill out.  I am calm right now rather content.  Lets keep it that way, hopefully.  *sigh* Here we go.   Let's do this...

Um it's wednesday.  Oh yay.  I am so friggin bored.  There is absolutely nothing to do ever!  We have to leave for work in like 10 minutes oh good times.  Blah.  Thats all for now then I guess.  Peace nugga.

Hmm well the weekend is over.  I have to go back to work today.  BLah argh.  Oh well its not too bad.  Its money and I love kids so...  This weekend uh what did we do. 

  • Friday we didn't have the car.
  • Saturday we had nothing to do.  Then we went to Kati's dad's and got on the internet.  We decided to go to John's house.  Amy went to the basement, Kati wondered around and me and John and Drew watched Napoleon Dynamite.  My 6th time yet still oh so funny.  We started to watch anchor man and then Amy and Kati came upstairs and said we were leaving.  It was like 3:30.  Then we went out and noticed it snowed a little.  We made it from fairfield to Middletown ok.  Then we almost wrecked it was scary.  We were hungry so we went to SnS.  MMMmmmm.  Then we got home about 6 or so.  Mammaw thought the car was broken down so luckily she didn't lock us out. 
  • Sunday we went to church, noone was there but Nick and his friend Seth.  Terrah didnt come cause she said I was going to beat her up.  Terrah if you read this I didn't say I would beat you up.  That's crazy I would go to jail and be really embarrassed for fighting at church.  Duh.  Then I am not sure what we did.  Kati and Amy took a nap, I couldn't sleep so I was texting John. Then they went and ate I stayed at home.
  • Monday we went and got Chris and went to Mcdonalds.  We made it to the mall to do a round of ddr and then John picked me up.  We went to his house and watched fight club.  He has mad skills he is almost as good of a cuddler as tony. Cuddling is my favorite. Lol.  It was fun. He is so adorible.  Totally not someone I would think would talk to me.  Amy seems much more his type than I do.  He played football and shit.  I am glad he talks to me though he smells real good haha. He's real nice. Then I went home, ate some leftover spaghetti MMmmm and fell asleep on the couch for like 3 hours til Amy got home and took me to Aprils.
  • Tuesday I am at Aprils.  I have to go to work, then I will probably do nothing.  I do need to walk over to Mcgees.  Fun times.  Its real freaking cold out.  Ah.

Blah I am so tired.  Life sucks hardcore as usual.  Being single is friggin retarded, I hate it.  Oh well whatever.  I am good.  Well not really, but better than I was that's for sure.  I don't know.  Well work is going pretty good.  I like it ok.  I have actually worked two weeks and not puked or anything.  That's good for me.  Lol.  Amy's car needs fixed and we actually have people who said they would fix it.  That's a first.  I am so glad though.  It shouldn't cost a lot either.  We get paid today so I think it will be ok.  I am friggin hungry.  What's new?  Lol.  I need to get laid, it's real bad.   Haha.  Not going to happen I guess.  That's ok though.  Ok then fun times.

Blah it's thursday and I guess it's been ruined.  Work was ok today.  I like it I guess.  Me and Cathy are friends now lol.  Not really.  It's not even 8:30 yet.  I am super tired.  I have to babysit tomorrow so I am staying at April's tonight.  I would rather sleep in my own bed.  I really need to do it.  Anyone?  No?  Ok then.  I guess I should probably get drunk this weekend.  I get paid tomorrow.  I owe Amy and my Grandma money.  Oh well.  Hhmmmm...  Again anyone wanna do it?  No still ok.   Alright then fun times in the neighborhood.

I am trying to be ok, but I am just not.  I don't want to pretend like I am because it doesn't do any good.  I don't like this at all.  I am sad and hurt and upset and angry.  Alot with myself for the way I am.  I don't want to pretend anymore, but I don't know what else to do.

Not good times.  I couldn't feel any worse than I do right now and that's the worst feeling in the world.

Well I haven't updated in a while.  So what's new?  I started work this past Monday.  It's going pretty good.  I like it.  I have a pretty good time and the kids are adorable.  Noah oh what can I say about him.  He is awesome.  He is so cute and Tony, him and Molly would be a cute couple.  Lol.  The kids are great.  It actually makes me want to have a baby instead of not.  They are all just so cute and funny.  Kids are super awesome.  I want a baby.  Not now of course, but sometime.  John will you have my baby?  Lol.  That would be crazy.  Anyways...  I stayed at John's last night, we had a pretty good time if I should say so myself.  I know he did.  He was with me duh. The other night me and Amy and Butch went to John's.  Shrek was there.  Shrek you suck.  Lol.  Butch did an industrial piercing on me, I almost vomited.  Yes it hurt that bad.  Ok then well that's all the fun for now.  Good times.

 

 That of course is not my ear, but that is what it looks like.
I totally wish I was fucking dead right now
I am such a friggin idiot gosh!

Blah I am super stressed out today.  ARGH.  I hate being by myself when I am mad.  Oh well.  I am staying at John's tonight.  He is probably totally fucking sick of me.  I am not sick of him though.  I think I am too clingy I guess.  I don't know what my problem is.  It's like if I don't see him for a couple days I freak out or something like I won't see him again.  I guess I know why I am like that.  It's like my grandma is the only person I have left you know other than Amy and Chris, and alls we do is fight.  I totally hate it.  I really hate this.  I miss my mom and dad.  This super sucks.  I hate crying.  I just wish everything would be ok.  I think I need to be put on prozac or something.  I mean John makes me super happy, but he is going to think I am friggin crazy or something and get totally sick of me being around that's always what happens.  Can't people understand that I just want someone to be there for me?  I guess I just need to calm down and take a deep breath and realize everything isn't always going to go my way or be how I want it to.  AHHHHHHHHHH.  I need to get laid.

Hmmm it's almost the fucking new year yay.  Fun times.  I am sitting at John's with Amy.  He is drunk somewhere.  Lol.  I am close to drunk here.  Maybe a little more than close.  I don't know geez.  I wish John was home so I could fucking do him.  Yeah Do him.  Ahaha.  I am going to stay over here tomorrow so I can do him duh.  Do it.  That's funny.  Blah.  Haha I can't even type.  I need some fucking cigarettes or something.  I lost a pack I don't know where.  I am retarded.  Duh retarded.  I am talking to Kati.  She is crazy.  I wish I had a burrito or something.   That's what I need right now.  I am so fucking fat.  One minute til the new year oh yay.  I don't even have anyone to make out with.  Thanks John.  I can't freakin believe it it's the new year.  Who fucking cares?  I just want to do it.  I love you John duh.  Let's do it.  Argh  Happy New Year you fucking fucks.  You know what else I friggin love?  Fucking Mr. Nelly Bubbles.  I freakin love that fish.  I think we have bonded. 

That kinda looks like Nelly, but Mr. Bubbles is so much cuter.  Duh.

Well it's new years eve and it totally fucking sucks.  I have nothing to do tonight like usual.  I should go out and get really fucking drunk, but I have no money or no one to go with.  Life sucks as always, but what's new?  Fucking nothing.  Blah...  I am tired and really super bored.  I miss John, but he is hanging out with his friends tonight, doing what or who I don't really know.  Lol.  I wish I had some damn friends.  Oh well I probably don't because I would just fight with them like everyone else.  I need some cash quick.  I will be so glad when I start work.  I will still be watching Annah too so I should bring in about close to 500 every two weeks which is alot more than 150.  Excited about that.  I need to move out.  Does anyone want to live with me?  That's a silly question, no one could put up with me.  You know one of my skills is whining.  Haha.  Well according to Kati one is deep throating too.  Lol so maybe some takers.  Just kidding.  I wish I was drunk...

My drink of choice, good ole vodka.  Delicious.
Hmm I am tired.  Amy is looking at me.  She is crazy.  My stomach hurts and I am hungry.  Blah.  I wanna do it.

What's happening, she's not there
Just silence, the writing's on the wall
